  "time_ut": 1661099944,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbd \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Say goodbye to politics when appropriate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Mahinda Rajapaksa said that he will retire from politics when the time is right.",
        "The former president said this while giving an interview to the Sunday Times newspaper.",
        "The former president said that it is up to the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna to decide whether he wants to lead and said that he is ready to step down if necessary.",
        "He pointed out that being a lawyer, he can also engage in court work.",
        "He also stated that if he had been asked while leaving the country, he would have informed Mr. Gotabaya Rajapakse not to leave the country.",
        "\u201cIf he had asked me to go, I would have said no. Gotabhaya is not a politician. Gotabaya Rajapakse is not responsible for all the disasters in the country. The past governments, including myself, must answer all these.",
        "Unfortunately, he acted on the advice of experts he trusted. So he can't be blamed. He showed good administrative skills while working as the Defense Secretary.",
        "As the president, he was under a lot of pressure. He used to be a bigot. Later he mellowed. He should not have done what he did. Gotabaya is not a politician. He should have finished the task before him properly.\"",
        "Mr. Mahinda Rajapaksa said that Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe is the best leader to manage the economic crisis and said that he will give him all the support.",
        "At this time, the former president further said that all political parties should come together to solve the country's problem and everyone should work with one opinion for the country."
      ],
